'''摩根·内维尔'''（{{lang-en|Morgan Neville}}，{{bd|1967年|10月10日||}}）<ref name="filmreference">{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/52/Morgan-Neville.html |title=Morgan Neville Biography (1967-) |work=filmreference.com |year=2014 |accessdate=February 24, 2014 |archive-date=2018-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004161705/http://www.filmreference.com/film/52/Morgan-Neville.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一名美国电影监制、导演和编剧。

== 生平 ==
内维尔生于加州[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]，原先他是一名在[[纽约市|纽约市]]和[[旧金山|旧金山]]工作的[[记者|记者]]<ref name="tremolo">{{cite web |url=http://tremoloproductions.com/about-us/ |title=Morgan Neville |work=Tremolo Productions |year=2014 |accessdate=February 24, 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227193626/http://tremoloproductions.com/about-us/ |archivedate=2014年2月27日 }}</ref>，1993年转行进入电影事业。他的导演处女作是一部纪录片 ''Shotgun Freeway: Drives thru Lost L.A'' (1995)<ref name="filmreference"/>，随后制作了一系列有关音乐人的纪录片。他曾分别凭借 ''Muddy Waters: Can't Be Satisfied'', ''Respect Yourself: The Stax Records Story'', 和 ''Johnny Cash's America'' 获得过三次[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名<ref name="tremolo"/>；2008年导演的 ''The Cool School'' 是一部有关洛杉矶当代艺术起源的纪录片，在克里夫兰国际影展上亮相。

2013年执导的音乐纪录片《[[离巨星二十英尺|离巨星二十英尺]]》赢得[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳纪录片奖<ref>{{cite web |first=Andrew |last=Pulver |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/mar/03/20-feet-from-stardom-wins-best-documentary-oscar |title=20 Feet from Stardom wins best documentary Oscar |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=March 3, 2014 |accessdate=March 3, 2014 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201044502/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/mar/03/20-feet-from-stardom-wins-best-documentary-oscar |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Mark |last=Olsen |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-2014-documentary-winner-20-feet-from-stardom-20140302,0,2870856.story |title=Oscars 2014: '20 Feet From Stardom' wins for documentary |work=[[LA_Times|LA Times]] |date=March 2, 2014 |accessdate=March February 3, 2014 |archive-date=2014-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422183917/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-2014-documentary-winner-20-feet-from-stardom-20140302,0,2870856.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

